  "comment": "Helios Multifunctional Outdoor Uplight Kit: The Helios kit is a set consisting of an indoor/outdoor uplight unit with built-in battery and, in addition to an attachable finishing ring, a number of decorative set up units, including a sphere and a tube effect. These decorative attachments can easily be mounted onto the uplight using a magnetic closure. The uplight is equipped with 6x 15W high efficiency RGBWA-UV LEDs to create a bright, intense and powerful color spectrum, and can be controlled via wireless DMX or via Wi-Fi (App). When fully charged, this uplight can last up to 15 hours (depending on color and intensity), and the charging time is approximately 8 hours. This uplight is silent, as no fan is used.\n\n",
